metadata.name: mfers club #2
metadata.description: We are the mfers club.  6666 mfers club roaming in the blockchain having different traits.  No official discord. No roadmap. No drama ,Just mfing club vibes! Like Sartoshi said, “there is no king, ruler, or defined roadmap--and mfers can build whatever they can think of with these mfers”.mfers club are a derivative collection created by mfers club teams and inspired by sartoshi's mfers.  mfers club are generated entirely from hand drawings. This project is in the public domain; feel free to use mfers any way you want.
